==应用==
SEA-ME-WE 4用于达成“电话、互联网、多媒体及各种宽带数据应用”。<ref name="project_about" />SEA-ME-WE 3与SEA-ME-WE 4光缆系统旨在为彼此提供冗余能力。<ref name="project_about" />两条光缆系统互相独立但相辅相成，四号并非用于取代三号系统。<ref name="project_about" />两者的设备来自同一个项目——{{tsl|en|SEA-ME-WE}}，但有着不同的着重点。SEA-ME-WE 3远远超过39000公里<ref name="REACH">{{cite web |title=Mediterranean Cable Break |url=http://www.reach.com/network/overview.php |accessdate=2008-02-01 |work=REACH : Network |publisher=Reach Global Services Limited |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070621165753/http://reach.com/network/overview.php |archivedate=2007-06-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>（相较SEA-ME-WE 4的18,800公里）并从日本和澳大利亚沿[[歐亞大陸板塊|歐亞大陸板塊]]底部延伸到爱尔兰和德国。<ref name="SEA-ME-WE3_config">{{cite web |url=http://www.seamewe3.com/inpages/cable_system.asp |title=Cable System Configuration |accessdate=2008-02-01 |work=South East Asia-Middle East-Western Europe 3 |publisher=Sri Lanka Telecom |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070714175845/http://www.seamewe3.com/inpages/cable_system.asp |archivedate=2007-07-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>SEA-ME-WE 4有比SEA-ME-WE 3更快的数据传输速率，速度达1.28 Tbit/s而非SEA-ME-WE 3的0.96 Tbit/s。<ref name="REACH" />SEA-ME-WE 3将连接提供到了更远距离的更多国家，但SEA-ME-WE 4提供了更高的数据传输速度，适应[[发展中国家|发展中国家]]对高速互联网接入不断增长的需求。<ref name="project_about" />

==技术==
该光缆使用[[波分复用|密集波分多路复用]]（DWDM），<ref name="NAS_about" />与承载非复用信号的光纤相比能增加每个光纤的通信容量，并且促进单个光纤内的双向通信。DWDM在单根光纤上采用不同的[[激光|激光]][[波长|波长]]完成[[多路复用|多路复用]]，因此多路{{tsl|en|Optical Carrier|光载体}}信号可以同时沿这根光纤传输。每对光纤使用两根光纤维，能够承载64个载波，每个10Gbit/s。<ref name="Fujitsu" />这使SEA-WE-ME 4光缆有着近每秒太比特（Tbit/s）的速度，<ref name="project_about" />，总容量1.28 Tbit/s。<ref name="Fujitsu" />2011年2月，联合体按合约将段落能力升级至40 Gbit/s每链路，登陆站设备能力将随需要升级至100 Gbit/s。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fiercetelecom.com/story/alcatel-lucent-ciena-conduct-upgrades-sea-me-we-4-cable-system/2011-02-01?utm_medium=rss&utm_source=rss |title=Alcatel-Lucent, Ciena to conduct upgrades for SEA-ME-WE 4 cable system - FierceTelecom<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2017-01-03 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304071711/http://www.fiercetelecom.com/story/alcatel-lucent-ciena-conduct-upgrades-sea-me-we-4-cable-system/2011-02-01?utm_medium=rss&utm_source=rss |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2015年2月3日，[[三菱电机|三菱电机]]宣布已完成“South East Asia ─ Middle East ─ Western Europe 4（SEA-ME-WE 4）”光缆系统的升级和扩展。
三菱电机为全部16个登陆站提供了具有incorporated superior coherent技术的100G MF-6900GWS海底线路终端设备（SLTE），以升级目前的40吉比特每秒（Gbps）电缆系统为100Gbit/s，并将最终设计能力从2,800Gbit/s扩展至4,600Gbit/s。新的SLTE将每个机架的数据能力翻倍，并降低了47%电力消耗。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mitsubishielectric.com/news/2015/pdf/0318.pdf |title=Mitsubishi Electric Completes Upgrade of SEA-ME-WE 4 Network - Data capacity of the submarine network is increased significantly with 100G technologies |accessdate=2017-01-03 |archive-date=2016-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009151538/http://www.mitsubishielectric.com/news/2015/pdf/0318.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

